Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.22,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:355488,357224}I almost feel sorry for her.{NOTE:かわいいそうだったかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:00.62,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:357224,360627}No, no. I can't forget\Nhow she played me.{NOTE:いやいや どうこした 悪戯を甘やかすのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.22,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:360627,362229}Stupid kid.{NOTE:バカな子だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.66,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:364831,366666}That was a little too cruel.{NOTE:ちょっと酷すぎるわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.80,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:366666,367801}You think so, too?{NOTE:そう思うだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.97,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:367801,369970}I was referring to you, Junshou.{NOTE:違う じゅんしょう だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.40,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:369970,371404}I know.{NOTE:分かってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.00,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:371404,374007}I feel sorry for her\Nfor having left without a pair.{NOTE:… なんてかわいそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.14,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:374007,375141}You're right.{NOTE:そうなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.07,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:375141,377077}In the end I felt the same way.{NOTE:俺だって落ち込んでる}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:21.48,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:377077,381481}Maybe you saw your old self in her.{NOTE:じゅんしょう はその子に自分の昔の姿を見たんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.11,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:381481,384117}Perhaps that's why you got angry.{NOTE:だから余計 腹が立ったのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.52,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:384918,388521}You were quite mischievous yourself\Nwhen you were little, Junshou.{NOTE:クレモナ から 住所によく意地悪されたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.62,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:388521,389623}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.02,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:389623,392025}I was an unruly, bad kid.{NOTE:俺は手に負えない 悪ガキ だったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.49,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:393193,394494}Sorry, sorry.{NOTE:ごめんごめん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.89,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:394494,395896}Don't get depressed.{NOTE:落ち込まないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.39,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:395896,397397}I won't say it anymore.{NOTE:もう言わないから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.76,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:398398,400767}Snow… I wonder if it piles up.{NOTE:雪つもるかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.53,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:401902,406539}Bouya-kun, you said I'm not interested\Nin women, but that's not true.{NOTE:ぼうやくん 俺が女に興味ないなんてとんでもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.94,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:406539,407941}What I want to say is…{NOTE:つまり}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:53.81,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:407941,413813}We've been together since we were little\Nand I've never noticed anyone else.{NOTE:ここ数年間 この二つ年上の幼なじみがいない 全く目に入らないってことなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:59.11,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:415148,419119}But she doesn't seem to have noticed.{NOTE:彼女の方が全く気づいていないけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.73,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:430230,432732}I wonder when\Nsomeone will move in.{NOTE:いつ越してくるんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:18.53,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:432732,438538}As a matter of fact, Junshou, it seems\Nthat there is someone living there already.{NOTE:じゅんしょう そのことだが どうも 誰か住んでるみたいなんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.74,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:438538,441741}But there are no signs of anyone yet.{NOTE:人の気配がしないもの まだだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.07,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:441741,443076}It's an empty house.{NOTE:空き家だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.14,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:443076,444144}No.{NOTE:いや}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.98,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:444144,447981}Yesterday I saw that\Nthe light was on.{NOTE:昨夜はかりがチラチラしているのを私は見たんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.38,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:447981,449382}It could be a thief.{NOTE:泥棒 かもしれん}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.08,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:449382,450083}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.01,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:450083,453019}Dad, you're making me worry.{NOTE:お父さん 勇気ある行動ですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.48,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:453019,456489}No, if something happens,\NI'll call the police immediately.{NOTE:何かあったらすぐ警察に連絡できるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.15,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:456489,458158}Telephone number\Nis enough for me.{NOTE:私の電話番号をしていいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:44.36,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:459592,464364}Which means you want me\Nto go take a look, right?{NOTE:ということは俺が見てくるっていうことなんだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.87,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:476142,477877}It's a nice house.{NOTE:可愛い家だよな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.04,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:477877,481047}A pink roof and white walls.{NOTE:ピンクの屋根に白い壁だもんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.61,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:482916,484617}Wow, it's not locked?{NOTE:あっ かかってないのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.35,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:488822,490357}It's too nice.{NOTE:かわいすぎる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.49,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:490357,494494}Looks like the owner\Nwas a wealthy one.{NOTE:こういうのに限って 持ち主は禿げたおっさんだったりするんだよな}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.76,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:494494,496763}But there's no furniture.{NOTE:家具 なんか何もないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.46,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:496763,498465}I knew it. Not a soul.{NOTE:やっぱりまだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:18.96,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:498465,498965}Hm?{NOTE:¿Hm?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.18,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:517083,518184}Who are you?{NOTE:あなた誰}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.05,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:518184,519052}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.95,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:520687,522956}Do you want something?{NOTE:家に何か御用}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.52,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:522956,525525}I-I'm from the temple next door.{NOTE:と、隣のお寺のものですけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.29,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:527026,529295}Have you come to give me\Nan amulet or something?{NOTE:…を貰いにでも来たの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.23,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:529295,533233}N-No. We thought we saw someone,\Nand thought it might be a thief.{NOTE:い、いいえ 人の気配がするんで 泥棒 かと 思って}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.83,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:534334,536836}I moved in here three days ago.{NOTE:3日前にこの家に来たのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.13,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:536836,539139}I-I see. I apologize.{NOTE:そうですか すみません}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.07,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:539139,541074}I've entered without permission.{NOTE:勝手に上がり込んだりして}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.87,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:542409,543877}How cold…{NOTE:寒い}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:08.64,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:543877,548648}There's no stove.\NAlso, she looks like she's still a child.{NOTE:ストーブも何もない それにまだ子供じゃないのかな この子}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.98,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:550483,552986}Can this even be called moving in?{NOTE:これで引っ越してきたなんて言えるかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:24.79,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:559559,564798}A shoe store clerk during the day, a thief\Nduring the night. And maybe a homosexual?{NOTE:昼間は靴屋の店員 夜は泥棒 そして ホモか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.33,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:566599,567333}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.83,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:567333,570837}Y-You see, my work at the\Nshoe store is a part-time job.{NOTE:あ、あのね 僕はね靴屋の店員はアルバイトで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:34.67,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:570837,574674}There was no sign of anyone moving in\Nand we saw someone's presence here,{NOTE:これは筆耕しの気配ないし 隣の家からは誰がいるようだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.77,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:574674,576776}I thought it would be terrible\Nif there was fire.{NOTE:もし火事でも出たらその大変だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.94,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:577877,580947}Funny how you want to\Nexplain everything at once.{NOTE:一番に説明しようとしてるのおもしろい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:44.61,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:580947,584617}I'm neither a thief nor a homosexual.{NOTE:僕はね 泥棒じゃないし 断じてホモでもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.86,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:593893,595862}Do you want me to believe you?{NOTE:信じてほしい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:59.39,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:595862,599399}What about you?\NAre you really from this family?{NOTE:君こそ本当にこの家の人}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:04.40,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:599399,604404}You know, you may look nice when you smile,\Nbut you're a pretty bad person, aren't you?{NOTE:あなたってね 痩せそうに笑うけど 本当はとっても意地悪ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:12.37,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:608608,612378}You actually did have those red boots\Nin my size, didn't you?{NOTE:本当はあの赤い靴 あったんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.54,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:613179,615548}I apologize for that.{NOTE:わるかった あれは}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.85,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:615548,618852}But you remember\Nwhat happened before, right?{NOTE:でもその前の自分のこと 君を覚えてるだろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.42,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:620120,621421}Of course.{NOTE:覚えてるわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.02,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:621421,624023}Yes, I've been pretty bad, too.{NOTE:そうよ 私すごく意地悪なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.89,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:624023,625892}But you're no better.{NOTE:でもあなたもそうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.56,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:625892,629562}If you were a good person,\Nyou wouldn't have retaliated.{NOTE:本当に優しい人なら仕返しなんかしないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.26,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:629562,632265}You wouldn't have done\Nsomething like that.{NOTE:こんな子供のやったことなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.26,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:632265,634267}You're not nice at all,{NOTE:やさしくないのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.70,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:634267,635702}and yet you pretend you are.{NOTE:やさし…して}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.17,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:640006,642175}Go away and become\Na better person.{NOTE:帰って！何よ土足で}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.04,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:642175,643042}Oh!{NOTE:あっ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:55.32,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:651117,655321}It's a pity there's nothing here\Nfor you to steal, Mr. Thief.{NOTE:収穫なしじゃ かわいそうだもんね 泥棒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.19,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:655321,657190}What a nasty girl.{NOTE:なんて嫌な子だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.56,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:663563,665565}You're not nice at all.{NOTE:あなた意地悪だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.83,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:666666,669836}I don't have to worry\Nabout what that girl says to me.{NOTE:気にするな あんなこと言ったことなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.33,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:669836,672338}I used to hear\Nthat stuff a lot in the past.{NOTE:あんなことは昔よく言われたもんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.44,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:673239,676442}Even Seiko told me\Nthat I was a really mean boy.{NOTE:俺は本当に悪ガキでそういう子だって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.81,Alternative,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:677610,680813}I hate bullies like you, Junshou!{NOTE:じゅんしょうなんて 私苛めっ子大嫌い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.11,Alternative,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:680813,682115}I hate you!{NOTE:大嫌いよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:27.25,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:682882,687253}Those words hurt me,\Nbut I can't tell Seiko how it felt.{NOTE:あの言葉が気になって そういうに俺の気持ちを打ち明けられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.22,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:691190,693226}Junshou, do you have a moment?{NOTE:じゅんしょう ちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.62,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:693226,696629}Our new neighbor who just moved in\Nhas come to greet us.{NOTE:隣の方が引越しの挨拶に来られてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:40.20,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:696629,700200}She says you left\Nsomething yesterday.{NOTE:それと 昨日お前が忘れ物をしたって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.43,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:700200,701434}I left something?{NOTE:忘れ物}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.94,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:705605,708942}So the scarf wasn't yours.{NOTE:なんだ マフラー あなたのじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.34,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:708942,711344}If it's not yours, it must be his.{NOTE:あなたのじゃなきゃ 彼のだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.54,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:714514,716549}So that's how it was.{NOTE:なんだそうだったのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.95,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:716549,717951}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:58.95,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:717951,718952}I'm leaving now.{NOTE:じゃあ これで}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.42,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:718952,721421}Ah, you can stay a little longer.{NOTE:ああ ゆっくりしていったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.49,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:721421,724490}I just came to make sure.{NOTE:ちょっと 確かめたかっただけだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.89,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:724490,726893}My father is preparing tea.{NOTE:今オヤジがお茶入れてるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.20,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:737570,740206}What's your name?{NOTE:名前 何という？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.50,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:740840,742508}Tateno Mizuki.{NOTE:たての みずき}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:26.37,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:742508,746379}And you're Fujioka Junshou, right?{NOTE:あなた 藤岡じゅんしょうってい うんでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.44,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:746379,748448}You're going to become\Na monk, aren't you?{NOTE:お坊さんになるんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:32.18,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:748948,752185}No, this temple will go\Nto my little brother.{NOTE:いやこの寺 は弟が継ぐから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.82,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:752185,754821}He's at the University\Nof Tokyo now, though.{NOTE:今は東京の大学にいってるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.52,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:754821,757523}Oh, it should be you.{NOTE:あら あなたが継げばいいのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:43.89,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:757523,763896}It'd be perfect. The shape of your head is just right\Nand in a few years you'll make a great baldie.{NOTE:きっとお似合いわよ 頭うっそうだし そらなくても数年後にはそのまま 立派な丸禿だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.97,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:772739,773973}You seem to have fun.{NOTE:楽しそうですね}
