Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:12.95,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:788454,792959}I like being alone, and I play outside\Nin the daytime anyway.{NOTE:私1人の方が好きだし どうせ 昼間は外で遊んでるから}
