Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:18.89,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:797764,798898}College?{NOTE:大学？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:21.23,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:798898,801234}But she doesn't look older\Nthan a high school student.{NOTE:中学生にしか見えないじゃないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.10,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:801234,804103}I'm already in the fourth grade.\NI'm graduating this spring anyway.{NOTE:4年生だから どうせこの春 卒業 だし}
