Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:48.02,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:824090,828027}You had to retake the year once,\Nso that makes you the same age.{NOTE:じゅんしょうは一浪してるから じゃあ 同い年なのね}
