Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.33,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:836769,838338}That's pretty selfish.{NOTE:わがままね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.87,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:838338,840873}She's selfish, but in a cute way.{NOTE:わがままだけど可愛いわ}
