Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.56,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:862729,865565}What about you, Junshou?\NWhy don't you get a girlfriend?{NOTE:じゃあじゅんしょうこそ どうして恋人を作らないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.53,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:865565,866532}Uh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.46,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:866532,868468}Why?{NOTE:どうして？}
