Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.81,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:917550,918818}Junshou.{NOTE:じゅんしょうに}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.05,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:918818,921053}Junshou, I want you to stop me.{NOTE:じゅんしょうに止めてほしいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.72,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:921053,924724}The truth is… that I don't really want\Nyou to find any cute girls.{NOTE:可愛い子見つけなさいなんて本当は言いたくないのよ}
