Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.64,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181480,1183649}I wonder if she's there.{NOTE:あの子いるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:49.12,Alternative,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185051,1189121}During the day, I'm playing outside.\NI just come back at night.{NOTE:一日中遊んでいるから 夜何に変えるだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.02,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189822,1192024}I wonder if she has any friends?{NOTE:あの子にも友達いるのかな}
