Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.39,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293659,1295394}Are you really a college student?{NOTE:きみ大学生って本当？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.53,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295394,1297530}I'm Hibino, the baker\Nfrom the Second Street.{NOTE:僕2丁目のケーキ屋の日比野です}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.03,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297530,1300032}I'm still single.\NPleased to meet you.{NOTE:俺未だ一人もんです よろしくね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.60,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301133,1302601}Nice to meet you.{NOTE:よろしく}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.26,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302601,1303269}Here.{NOTE:はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303269,1305738}Alright, let's get this party started!{NOTE:よし婚約パーティーのやり直し}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:46.93,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1305738,1306939}Cheers!{NOTE:乾杯！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.50,Default,Bouya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306939,1309508}I'll sing a love song for you.{NOTE:では 二人のために 愛の歌を}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.14,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309508,1311143}Do you want some juice?{NOTE:ジュースはいい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.51,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311143,1312511}No need for that.{NOTE:…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.38,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320119,1322388}She's awfully quiet today.{NOTE:今日はやけに大人しいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:07.89,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326792,1327893}You know…{NOTE:私ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:08.86,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327893,1328861}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.89,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328861,1330896}I hate this kind of thing.{NOTE:こういうの大嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.56,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330896,1333566}An engagement party?\NYou're too ridiculous.{NOTE:婚約パーティーなんてバカみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.83,Default,Bouya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333566,1334834}What?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:20.90,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339438,1340906}I'm going.{NOTE:帰るわ やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.00,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340906,1342007}Will you walk me back?{NOTE:送ってくれる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:22.97,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342007,1342975}No.{NOTE:いいやだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:28.44,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345177,1348447}Is it payback for my payback\Nfor your payback?{NOTE:それは仕返しの仕返しの仕返しのつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.71,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349515,1351717}Stop saying garbage.{NOTE:嫌な言い方するなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:35.45,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351717,1355454}I invited you here because I thought\Nyou'd feel lonely, being alone in that house.{NOTE:あの家に一人でいて 寂しいだろうと思って 読んだんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.72,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355454,1357723}If you didn't want to come,\Nyou could've just said so.{NOTE:嫌なら来なきぇよかったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:43.22,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362228,1363229}I'm leaving.{NOTE:帰る}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:46.69,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364897,1366699}Hold on.{NOTE:待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.60,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366699,1368601}Junshou, I'm going with her.{NOTE:じゅんしょ私は送っていくわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.93,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368601,1370936}She's living next door.\NShe can go back by herself.{NOTE:隣なんだから一人で帰れるだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:52.03,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370936,1372037}But…{NOTE:でも！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.74,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1379345,1381747}I must look like a little kid\Nto you, right?{NOTE:子供みたいに見えるでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.18,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381747,1383182}Especially when\NI'm with more people.{NOTE:みんなの中に入ると}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:05.88,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1383182,1385884}No, you didn't like one to me at all.{NOTE:いいえそんな風には見えなかったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:09.98,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385884,1389989}You know, when the year begins,\NI'll be moving in to the temple.{NOTE:あのね 私年が明けたら お寺に引っ越してくるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:13.82,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389989,1393826}We've yet to marry, but we've decided\Nto live together before that.{NOTE:結婚式はまだ先だけど一緒に住むことにしたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:17.16,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393826,1397162}We'll look for a flat\Nonce he graduates.{NOTE:彼が卒業したら二人でアパートを探すの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.00,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397162,1401000}This means we'll be\Nneighbors for a while.{NOTE:だから しばらく私たちは 隣同士}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.60,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401000,1402601}Let's be friends, okay?{NOTE:仲良くしましょうね}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.97,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404970,1406972}You can't get married.{NOTE:結婚なんかできないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:31.14,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407973,1411143}You can't get married!{NOTE:あなた達は結婚なんかできないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:33.01,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411143,1413012}I won't let you!{NOTE:私邪魔してやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:48.12,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424990,1428127}I wonder if I did anything\Nto make her hold such a grudge?{NOTE:俺あの子にそんなに恨まれるようなことしたかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:51.49,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1429161,1431497}It's me that she's holding\Na grudge against.{NOTE:恨まれてるのは私だな}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:52.33,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1431497,1432331}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:53.69,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1432331,1433699}Never mind.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:59.03,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1433699,1439038}Look, it's already piled up so much.\NAnd it's not even Christmas yet.{NOTE:見て！もうこんなに積もっちゃった まだ クリスマス前なのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.77,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439038,1441774}Let's spend Christmas Day\Ntogether this year.{NOTE:今年のクリスマスは二人きりで過ごす}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:03.90,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441774,1443909}Let's forget about our\Nbad-mannered neighbor.{NOTE:隣のいじめって何か忘れた}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.41,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443909,1445411}Christmas…{NOTE:クリスマス}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:06.67,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1445411,1446679}That's wonderful.{NOTE:素敵ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:10.34,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446679,1450349}Christmas this year will be\Ndifferent from previous ones.{NOTE:今年のクリスマスはいつもと違うわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:13.08,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450349,1453085}For the first time,\Nit'll be this wonderful.{NOTE:こんな素敵なのって初めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:16.45,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1455254,1456455}What do you think?{NOTE:じゅんしょうは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:18.52,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457356,1458524}I feel the same way.{NOTE:俺も}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.53,0:24:29.30,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1467533,1469301}I hate snow.{NOTE:雪は嫌い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.37,0:24:35.20,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1472371,1475207}I hate when it's falling like this.{NOTE:こんな風に降る雪は嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:36.27,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1475207,1476275}When it's like this…{NOTE:こんな風に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:40.47,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1477910,1480479}Everything ends up\Nbeing totally white.{NOTE:何もかも白くしてしまわないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:43.81,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1481547,1483816}Everything seems to be going away.{NOTE:何もかも消してしまわないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:49.92,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1487786,1489922}How do you like these ornaments?{NOTE:どう？この飾り付け}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.72,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1489922,1491724}They look good.{NOTE:ああ なかなかだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:56.42,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1492524,1496428}I thought they were much bigger\Nwhen I was a kid.{NOTE:子供の頃見た時には もっと大きかったと思ったんだけどな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:25:00.53,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1496428,1500532}But even though it's been more\Nthan ten years, they're still fine.{NOTE:でも10年ぶりに出した形には どれも綺麗ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:03.63,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1500532,1503635}They remind me of my mother.{NOTE:母さんが丁寧にしまっておいてくれたからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.63,0:25:04.93,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1503635,1504937}I see.{NOTE:そっか}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:07.40,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1504937,1507406}They were there when she was alive.{NOTE:おばさんが生きてらした頃なのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.04,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1507406,1510042}Do you know what\Nthat girl's doing now?{NOTE:ねえ 彼女どうしてる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.04,0:25:14.24,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1510042,1514246}She must be doing something,\Nbecause we haven't seen her again.{NOTE:勇ましいこと言ってた割には 俺たちの前に姿を見せないな}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:17.58,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1514246,1517583}Tomorrow is Christmas Day.\NMaybe she'll be with her family.{NOTE:明日はクリスマスだけど親戚の家にでも入ってるかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:24.55,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1521286,1524556}Somehow it reminds me of her.{NOTE:なんだかこれ あの子みたいだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.99,0:25:34.76,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1532998,1534767}Looks like she's not here.{NOTE:いないかやっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.76,0:25:37.46,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1534767,1537469}Not that I needed\Nto come to check on her.{NOTE:わざわざ 確かめに来ることもなかったけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.53,0:25:41.77,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1540539,1541774}Why?{NOTE:どうして}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.14,0:25:46.91,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1543142,1546912}Why did I get the impression\Nthat she'd be inside, alone in the dark?{NOTE:いると思ってしまうんだろうあの暗闇の中に}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.71,0:25:52.01,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1549715,1552017}Careless as usual.{NOTE:相変わらず不用心だな}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.97,0:26:25.51,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1579978,1585517}{\t(3072,5517,\1c&HDFDFDF&\3c&HDFDFDF&\4c&HDFDFDF&)\fad(0,500)}The Oak and the Pleasant Wind\NTateno Ken'ichi{NOTE:かしの木とやさしい風\\N立野賢一}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.65,0:26:29.65,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1588654,1589655}Seiko!{NOTE:せいこ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.65,0:26:30.72,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1589655,1590722}Seiko!{NOTE:せいこ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.72,0:26:32.19,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1590722,1592191}Seiko!{NOTE:せいこ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.19,0:26:34.52,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1592191,1594526}W-What happened?{NOTE:まあ どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.52,0:26:36.72,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1594526,1596728}Seiko, could you prepare a futon?!{NOTE:せいこ 布団を…てくれないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.72,0:26:38.56,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1596728,1598564}And call a doctor!{NOTE:それと医者もだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.23,0:26:42.90,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1600232,1602901}She almost got pneumonia.{NOTE:もう少しで肺炎 起こしところだったって}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:44.20,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1602901,1604203}It's no wonder.{NOTE:当たり前だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:47.77,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1604203,1607773}It's winter and that house\Ndoesn't even have a stove.{NOTE:こんな冬にストーブ もなかったんだ あの家には}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:48.80,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1607773,1608807}That's why…{NOTE:だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.80,0:26:53.21,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1608807,1613212}That's why I can't say\NI didn't see it coming.{NOTE:だからこうなることぐらい 予想できたのに 俺にも}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:58.51,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1614713,1618517}I don't know what this girl's thinking.{NOTE:分からないな この子の考えてること}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:01.95,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1618517,1621954}Sleeping like that on a cold floor.{NOTE:あんな風に冷たい床の上に眠るように}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.82,0:27:05.19,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1623822,1625190}Junshou, come here for a minute.{NOTE:じゅんしょう ちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.62,0:27:08.86,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1626625,1628861}They just called from the hospital.{NOTE:今の電話 病院からだったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.86,0:27:10.16,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1628861,1630162}From the hospital?{NOTE:病院？}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.16,0:27:14.23,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1630162,1634233}It seems her father has passed away.{NOTE:彼女のお父さんがね なくなったそうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.23,0:27:15.83,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1634233,1635834}He's dead?!{NOTE:死んだ？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.83,0:27:17.00,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1635834,1637002}What do we do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:19.20,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1637002,1639204}Should we wake her up?{NOTE:今あの子に知らせるべきかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.20,0:27:20.40,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1639204,1640405}No.{NOTE:いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.40,0:27:22.77,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1640405,1642774}Let's tell her after\Nthe fever goes down a little.{NOTE:もう少し熱が下がってからにしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.78,0:27:31.95,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1649781,1651950}She's become completely alone.{NOTE:ひとりぼっちになっちまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.22,0:27:42.49,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1661226,1662494}It's amazing.{NOTE:すごいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.49,0:27:45.59,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1662494,1665597}The fever went down\Nto 38°C overnight.{NOTE:一晩で38°まで下がった}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:48.36,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1666064,1668367}Where's my coat?{NOTE:私のコートどこ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.36,0:27:49.63,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1668367,1669635}You shouldn't be up yet.{NOTE:まだ無理だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.63,0:27:51.33,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1669635,1671336}You should rest for a little longer.{NOTE:もうすこしこの家で}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.87,0:27:55.20,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1672871,1675207}I have to go see my father.{NOTE:お父さんの所に行かなきゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:57.17,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1675207,1677176}I have to see if it's his face, at least.{NOTE:顔ぐらい見てあげなきゃね}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.17,0:27:58.07,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1677176,1678076}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.07,0:28:01.58,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1678076,1681580}I could hear you\Nfrom where you were talking.{NOTE:あんなところで立ち話してたら聞こえるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:02.91,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1681580,1682915}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめん}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.91,0:28:04.95,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1682915,1684950}Can you call a taxi for me?{NOTE:タクシー 拾ってくれる}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.95,0:28:06.05,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1684950,1686051}Wait a minute.{NOTE:ちょっと待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.05,0:28:09.35,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1686051,1689354}Even if it's gone down a bit,\Nyou're still running a fever of 38°C.{NOTE:熱が下がったから来てまだ38でも}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.35,0:28:10.68,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1689354,1690689}I hate being here.{NOTE:ここは嫌いなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:11.69,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1690689,1691690}Ah!{NOTE:あっ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.69,0:28:13.69,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1691690,1693692}Okay, I'll call a cab.{NOTE:じゃあ タクシーを拾うから}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.69,0:28:16.16,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1693692,1696161}But first, you have to eat something.{NOTE:その前に少し食事をしなきゃダメだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.16,0:28:18.06,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1696161,1698063}I'm not hungry.{NOTE:お腹すいてないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:26.10,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1704403,1706104}It's disgusting.{NOTE:まずい}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.10,0:28:29.34,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1706104,1709341}I'm sorry. I made it.{NOTE:悪かったね それ俺が作ったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.34,0:28:31.37,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1709341,1711376}I don't think it's bad, though.{NOTE:まずい分けないんだけどなあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.37,0:28:32.91,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1711376,1712911}Soups are my specialty.{NOTE:俺 おかゆ作るの得意だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.91,0:28:34.27,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1712911,1714279}But it is bad.{NOTE:だってまずいもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.27,0:28:37.38,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1714279,1717382}I hate porridge.\NI especially hate plums.{NOTE:お粥って大嫌い 梅干しも嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.38,0:28:41.65,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1717382,1721653}If you don't want to eat hospital food,\Nat least put a stove in that house.{NOTE:病院食が食べたくなければ あの家にストーブ 入れるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.65,0:28:43.48,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1721653,1723488}I hate stoves.{NOTE:ストーブ なんて嫌いよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:47.96,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1723488,1727960}I hate warmth\Nand I hate Christmas.{NOTE:あったかいの嫌いなの クリスマスも嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.09,0:28:51.93,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1730095,1731930}Today is Christmas Day.{NOTE:今日はクリスマス}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:54.60,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1731930,1734600}Even I have someone who loves me.{NOTE:こんな私でも愛してくれる人いるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.10,0:28:58.73,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1736101,1738737}I'm going to live with that person.{NOTE:私その人のところに行くの}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:06.21,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1742808,1746211}He's been taking care\Nof me for many years.{NOTE:もう何年も前から私のこと …に従ってるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.21,0:29:09.48,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1746211,1749481}He used to say I look very much\Nlike his late daughter.{NOTE:死んで娘さんによく似てるんですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.48,0:29:13.58,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1749481,1753585}See? Even if I don't have my father,\NI've got my next move figured out.{NOTE:ね？父親がいなくなっても 私の進路はちゃんと決まってるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.85,0:29:18.55,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1754853,1758557}There's nothing to worry about.\NSo don't feel sorry for me.{NOTE:何の心配もないわけ だからかわいそうなんて思わないでよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.79,0:29:22.59,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1759791,1762594}I already knew.{NOTE:私ちゃんと分かってた}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.63,0:29:29.20,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1765631,1769201}I knew my father wouldn't live long.{NOTE:お父さん長生きしないって}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.20,0:29:34.94,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1769201,1774940}That's why there's no stove\Nor furniture in that house.{NOTE:だからあの家にストーブも家具も何も用意する必要なんかなかったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.94,0:29:37.67,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1774940,1777676}Then what's that house for?{NOTE:じゃあ あの家は 何のためにあるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.67,0:29:39.04,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1777676,1779044}I don't know.{NOTE:知らない}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.04,0:29:41.78,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1779044,1781780}It was something\Nmy father had built.{NOTE:お父さんが勝手に建てたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.71,0:29:43.84,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1782714,1783849}That's all.{NOTE:それだけよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.05,0:29:46.71,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1785050,1786718}I'll call a taxi myself.{NOTE:自分でタクシー 拾うわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:47.81,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1786718,1787819}"That's all"?{NOTE:それだけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.81,0:29:48.88,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1787819,1788887}But…{NOTE:だって}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.85,0:29:53.19,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1791857,1793191}Hey, tell me something.{NOTE:ねえ 教えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.59,0:29:57.16,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1794593,1797162}How did you confess\Nyour feelings to Seiko-san?{NOTE:せいこさんに何て言って気持？ちを打ち明けたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.26,0:30:01.23,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1799264,1801233}How did you say it?{NOTE:どんな風に言ったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.23,0:30:04.83,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1801233,1804836}How do you tell a woman\Nthat you love her?{NOTE:あなた どんな風に女の人に愛を打ち明けるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.83,0:30:07.30,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1805837,1807306}Tell me.{NOTE:教えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.47,0:30:10.80,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1808473,1810809}I just told her "I love you".{NOTE:好きだ と言っただけだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:12.74,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1810809,1812744}And what did she say?{NOTE:そしたら せいこさんは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:14.78,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1812744,1814780}What did Seiko-san say to you?{NOTE:せいこさんは 何て言ったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.08,0:30:19.28,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1818083,1819284}"I love you".{NOTE:好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.55,0:30:22.55,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1821553,1822554}"I love you".{NOTE:好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:24.52,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1823388,1824523}That's what she told you, isn't it?{NOTE:そういったのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.82,0:30:28.99,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1827826,1828994}How boring.{NOTE:つまんない}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.99,0:30:30.49,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1828994,1830495}So simple.{NOTE:シンプルね}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.49,0:30:33.66,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1830495,1833665}Lovers' conversations are so stupid.{NOTE:恋人同士の会話 なんてバカみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.66,0:30:36.36,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1833665,1836368}If you found someone\Nthat you could love…{NOTE:君だって 好きな人ができれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.36,0:30:39.10,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1836368,1839104}I'll never find someone to love.{NOTE:好きな人なんて一生できないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.10,0:30:40.23,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1839104,1840238}Good bye.{NOTE:じゃあね}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.23,0:30:43.00,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1840238,1843008}Hold on. Do you want me\Nto go with you?{NOTE:待って！ついていこうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.00,0:30:45.34,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1843008,1845344}I'll be fine by myself.{NOTE:一人で大丈夫よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:56.08,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1854686,1856088}I feel strange.{NOTE:変な気分ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:31:05.86,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1857522,1865864}She's lost her father while we were decorating\Nthe Christmas tree and eating a cake.{NOTE:あの子が父親を亡くした夜に 私たちはクリスマスツリーを飾って ケーキを切って}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.86,0:31:07.69,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1865864,1867699}There's nothing we can do.{NOTE:仕方がないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.69,0:31:09.76,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1867699,1869768}She has to feel lonely.{NOTE:でも 心細いですよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.76,0:31:11.26,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1869768,1871269}And she still has a fever.{NOTE:未だ熱だっているのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.73,0:31:14.13,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1872738,1874139}Will she be all right?{NOTE:大丈夫かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.13,0:31:15.27,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1874139,1875273}You're right.{NOTE:そうだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.61,0:31:20.57,Alternative,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1879611,1880579}I love you.{NOTE:好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:23.71,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1882581,1883715}Junshou.{NOTE:じゅんしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.71,0:31:24.54,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1883715,1884549}Come with me for a bit.{NOTE:ちょっと来てくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.55,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1885484,1886551}In our temple?{NOTE:家の寺で}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.55,0:31:27.75,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1886551,1887753}Yes.{NOTE:ああ}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:29.98,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1887753,1889988}They just called us.{NOTE:たった今連絡があって}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.98,0:31:36.52,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1889988,1896528}When they told me, I was surprised,\Nbut it seems that I knew the father of that girl.{NOTE:それでなあ 聞いてびっくりしたんだけど 彼女の父親っていうのは ほれうちにもあったろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.52,0:31:38.83,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1896528,1898830}He was a writer\Nnamed Tateno Ken'ichi.{NOTE:たての けんいち っていう作家の本}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.83,0:31:40.23,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1898830,1900232}Tateno Ken'ichi?{NOTE:たての けんいち？}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:44.36,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1901233,1904369}{\fad(1000,0)}The Oak and the Pleasant Wind\NTateno Ken'ichi{NOTE:かしの木とやさしい風\\N立野賢一}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.87,0:31:48.57,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1904870,1908573}Oh, I think we have\None of his books, too.{NOTE:ああ 家にあるのは 「ドアのホン」だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:52.14,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1908573,1912144}He wrote nice stories\Nand I liked them a lot.{NOTE:あったかい話を書くんだよ 私は好きだったんだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.14,0:31:55.51,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1912144,1915514}But rumor has it he was\Na terrible alcoholic.{NOTE:噂では ひどいアル中だったらしいなあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.38,0:32:02.28,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1920385,1922287}The light is on.{NOTE:当たりがついてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.02,0:32:06.75,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1923021,1926758}There are a lot of parked cars.\NMust be the family.{NOTE:車もいっぱい 止まってたから 親戚が集まっているんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:09.36,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1928193,1929361}Still.{NOTE:それでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.53,0:32:12.96,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1931530,1932964}In there, that girl…{NOTE:その中で彼女は}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.16,0:32:17.00,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1934166,1937002}She's probably sitting all alone.{NOTE:やっぱり一人ぼっちなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.31,0:32:32.81,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1948313,1952818}Thank you for coming in this cold.{NOTE:寒いところありがとうございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:35.65,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1952818,1955654}Excuse me, where's Mizuki-san?{NOTE:あの みずきさんは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.65,0:32:40.12,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1955654,1960125}She still has a fever.\NShe's taking a rest at our house.{NOTE:まだ熱がありましてね 家の方で休んでるんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.12,0:32:42.82,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1960125,1962828}Of course she has,\Nwhen she's so reckless.{NOTE:当たり前だ 無茶ばっかりするから}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.96,0:32:47.23,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1963962,1967232}That's your specialty,\Nthe plum soup?{NOTE:じゅんしょう 特定の梅干し昆布茶 ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.23,0:32:49.80,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1967232,1969801}Good. I'll take it to Mizuki-san.{NOTE:いいわよ みずきさんに届けてくるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.80,0:32:50.86,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1969801,1970869}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめん}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:32:53.53,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1970869,1973538}I have to help my father, so…{NOTE:俺 親父を手伝わなきゃなんないから}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.53,0:32:54.73,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1973538,1974739}It's what she needs now.{NOTE:これは効くんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.73,0:32:56.77,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1974739,1976775}Even if she complains,\Nmake her eat it.{NOTE:文句言っても無理やり飲ませてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.77,0:32:57.84,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1976775,1977843}Fine, fine.{NOTE:はいはい}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:09.48,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1988086,1989488}Seiko's late.{NOTE:遅いなあ せいこう}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.25,0:33:15.39,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1993258,1995393}Maybe they're talking?{NOTE:話し込んでんのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.87,0:33:28.80,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2007873,2008807}Seiko!{NOTE:せいこ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.11,0:33:34.27,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2013111,2014279}No way…{NOTE:まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.44,0:33:37.71,Alternative,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2016448,2017716}I won't let you!{NOTE:私が邪魔してやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:40.18,Alternative,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2018283,2020185}It can't be!{NOTE:まさか そんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.69,0:33:46.59,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2025690,2026591}Seiko!{NOTE:せいこ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.16,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:2027993,2029160}Junshou!{NOTE:じゅんしょ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.32,0:33:51.09,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2030328,2031096}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.09,0:33:54.33,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:2031096,2034332}I suddenly saw fire\Nand I didn't know what to do.{NOTE:私 急に火が 何が何だか}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.33,0:33:55.23,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2034332,2035233}What about her?{NOTE:あの子は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.23,0:33:56.26,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:2035233,2036268}She's still inside.{NOTE:未だ中に}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.26,0:33:58.70,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:2036268,2038703}The fire came from the kitchen.\NI think she's there.{NOTE:台所から火が出た きっとそこに}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.70,0:34:00.23,Default,Seiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:2038703,2040238}Junshou!{NOTE:じゅんしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.02,0:34:21.12,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2060025,2061126}I…{NOTE:私}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.12,0:34:23.06,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2061126,2063061}Quick! Come here!{NOTE:速く！こっちへ来るんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.09,0:34:26.13,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2064095,2066131}What are you doing!? Hurry!{NOTE:何をするんだ？！速く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:28.03,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2066131,2068033}But you're angry, aren't you?{NOTE:だって怒るでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.36,0:34:30.53,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2069367,2070535}You are, aren't you?{NOTE:怒るでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.43,0:34:32.90,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2071436,2072904}I'm not.{NOTE:怒らないさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.90,0:34:34.77,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2072904,2074773}How could I be in this situation?{NOTE:こんなも…から}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.84,0:34:38.10,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2075840,2078109}Don't worry and come here.{NOTE:気にしないでこっちにお出で}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.10,0:34:39.91,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2078109,2079911}Come on, quick.{NOTE:さあ速く}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.23,0:35:02.66,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2101232,2102667}I…{NOTE:私…}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:08.40,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2102667,2108406}She showed me her father's book,\Nthen went crazy… Then the fire started.{NOTE:彼女のお父さんの本を見せてもらってて 夢中になってて そしたら火が}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.50,0:35:09.27,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2108506,2109274}Dad.{NOTE:父さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.47,0:35:12.01,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2110475,2112010}Dad…{NOTE:父さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.01,0:35:15.81,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2112010,2115814}Dad. Dad. Dad…{NOTE:父さん 父さん 父さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.61,0:35:19.38,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2116614,2119384}I was waiting for him, all alone.{NOTE:待ってたのに 一人で}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.38,0:35:22.28,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2119384,2122287}I've been waiting for him\Nall this time, in this house.{NOTE:ずっと待ってたのにこの家で}
