Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.00,0:35:42.54,Default,Fujioka Junshou's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:2139004,2142540}You played with fire and\Nhalf of the temple went up in smoke.{NOTE:火遊びでトラの半分も焼いてしまって}
