Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.70,0:36:49.57,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2205704,2209574}You know, Christmas Day…\NChristmas Day is my birthday.{NOTE:クリスマスはね 私の 私の誕生日なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.57,0:36:56.28,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2211576,2216281}Every year we were holding\Na party with Mom,{NOTE:毎年お母さんと二人で パーティーの用意をして}
