Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.81,0:37:02.48,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2218817,2222487}Today… Today he ought\Nto come back, too.{NOTE:今日こそは 今日こそは絶対ちゃんと帰ってくる}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.48,0:37:07.92,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2222487,2227926}Christmas Day is my birthday,\Nso it had to be today.{NOTE:だって クリスマスって私の誕生日だもの 今日だけは って思うでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.89,0:37:10.92,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2228893,2230929}And yet, he…{NOTE:なのにあの人はね}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:16.13,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2231763,2236134}He always came home in a bad mood\Nand tore the party apart.{NOTE:必ず寄って帰ってきて パーティーをめちゃめちゃにしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.13,0:37:20.37,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2236134,2240371}My mom died without having fun\Non Christmas Day even once.{NOTE:お母さんは いつでも楽しいクリスマスを迎えないまま死んだのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.27,0:37:24.74,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2241272,2244742}That's why I hate Dad the most.{NOTE:だから お父さん大嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.74,0:37:29.81,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2244742,2249814}I hate December. I hate Christmas.\NI hate my birthday!{NOTE:12月は嫌い クリスマスは嫌い 誕生日は嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.11,0:37:35.68,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2251116,2255687}If I didn't like anything\Nand never expected anything,{NOTE:何も好きになったり期待したりしなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.68,0:37:37.65,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2255687,2257655}no one would betray me either.{NOTE:裏切られることないんだもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.45,0:37:42.99,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2258456,2262994}But you were hoping your father\Nwould come back, right?{NOTE:でも君はお父さんが帰ってくるの待っていたんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.99,0:37:45.56,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2262994,2265563}You were waiting\Nfor him in that house.{NOTE:あの家で期待して}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:52.60,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2267065,2272604}Because he had to build that house\Nall of the sudden. That old fool.{NOTE:だってあの人 突然 あんな家 バカみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.60,0:37:58.30,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2272604,2278309}Long ago, I saw a house on a postcard\Nand said I'd like to live in it some day.{NOTE:昔私が 一度だけ住んでみたいって言った 絵葉書に書いてあった家を}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:37:59.47,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2278309,2279477}He remembered that.{NOTE:あの人 覚えてた}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.81,0:38:05.15,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2282814,2285150}I'll never grow up.{NOTE:私大人になれないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.15,0:38:07.28,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2285150,2287285}I'll always stay like this.{NOTE:いつまでもずっとこのままよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:14.65,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2287285,2294659}I've always felt like a little girl.\NI can never mature.{NOTE:私の気持ちはいつも子供の頃にしか帰らないの だからこのままずっと大人にはならないのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.65,0:38:19.66,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2294659,2299664}But I'm a nasty child, not nice at all,\Nso no one will ever want me.{NOTE:えも可愛げのない子供だから 誰も愛してなんかくれないわ}
