Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.06,0:38:27.90,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2304068,2307906}I behaved badly, I wasn't honest,\NI was always mischievous.{NOTE:ひねくれてて 淳じゃなくて 意地悪で}
