Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.24,0:38:39.45,Default,Fujioka Junshou,0,0,0,,{TIME:2315246,2319450}But, you know, even I wound up\Nbeing wanted by someone.{NOTE:でもね こんな俺でも ちゃんと愛してくれてた}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.45,0:38:41.65,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2319450,2321653}But I…{NOTE:でも私は}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.65,0:38:44.12,Default,Tateno Mizuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2321653,2324122}You hate me, don't you?!{NOTE:あなただって 私のこと嫌いでしょ}
